data.description:
Brick home with large lot...ranch-style home featuring 1,872 square feet and situated on 1.02-acre corner lot in the communty of Alexander (approx. 7 miles outside of Waynesboro). 
With updated kitchen, flooring and paint, this home offers an excellent move-in ready option with up to four bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Three spacious bedrooms are located on one end of the home, and a bonus room with a half-bath on the other end of the home could rerve as a large fourth bedroom. Large utility room and two rear exits (from utility room and bonus room). Double detached carport. Home is an easy commute to Waynesboro and Plant Vogtle.
